<div class="apiDetail">
<div>
	<h2><span class="path">treeHelper.</span>removeNodeById</h2>
	<h3>概述</h3>
	<div class="desc">
		<p></p>
		<div class="longdesc">
			<p>根据传入的id删除当前节点及其所有子节点。</p>
			<p class="highlight_red">id值为构建树时传入的数据中的id。</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<h3>Function 参数说明</h3>
	<div class="desc">
	<h4><b>id</b><span>number</span></h4>
	<h4 class="topLine"><b>返回值</b><span>Array []</span></h4>
	<p>返回删除后树的数据</p>
	</div>
	<h3>function 举例</h3>
	<pre xmlns=""><code>var tree = treeHelper.getTree("zyjg",{expandLevel : 1},[{id:1,text:"test",children[]}]);
var node = tree.removeNodeById(1);
</code></pre>
</div>
</div>